tests.name: twoFer() > no name given
tests.test_code: expect(twoFer()).toEqual('One for you, one for me.');

tests.name: twoFer() > a name given
tests.test_code:
const name = 'Alice';
expect(twoFer(name)).toEqual('One for Alice, one for me.');

tests.name: twoFer() > another name given
tests.test_code:
const name = 'Bob';
expect(twoFer(name)).toEqual('One for Bob, one for me.');
